   class HashIterator implements Iterator

    * hashtable during enumeration causes indeterminate results.  Don't do it!

    * @author       Jon Zeppieri
-   * @version      $Revision: 1.6 $

@@ -862,7 +862,7 @@ public Object nextElement()
       if (count >= size)
         throw new NoSuchElementException();
       count++;

       if (last != null)
